  <call-stmt>CALL <procedure-designator><named-E><N><n>C</n></N><R-LT><component-R>%<ct>PRINT</ct></component-R></R-LT></named-E></procedure-designator>(<arg-spec></arg-spec>)</call-stmt>

  <C>! Polymorphisme via CLASS</C>
  <call-stmt>CALL <procedure-designator><named-E><N><n>DESCRIBE</n></N></named-E></procedure-designator>(<arg-spec><arg><named-E><N><n>C</n></N></named-E></arg></arg-spec>)</call-stmt>
